                            },
                            "body": "Hello [~N200392] -san,\r\nThis ticket requires both works from LGE and HMI.\r\nIn short, HMI will trigger a new API on platform side (LGE) to send this signal to VKM: IVI_VK_Menu_operation_v2: 0b0110 (Owner key change start) \r\nI created a children story ticket to implement the new API on the platform side, so CRQ is required for this ticket.\r\n\r\nHello [~BSBE-TDB]-san, \r\nCurrenly, the platform side haven't discussed this new API with HMI yet. I kindly request HMI team to create a story ticket to confirm the final design of the new API. When the design of new API is agreed, we will start estimating and fill the plan.\r\n\r\nThank you!",
